records.name: Hondaafushi Island Resort

descriptions.direction: Hondaafushi is home to Hondaafushi Island Resort. Local points of interest include Utheemu Palace, Maldives Climate Observatory, and Baarah Dock.
descriptions.general: Hondaafushi Island Resort is full of greenery and sandy beaches. All our bungalows are fully detached and face the beach. Each bungalow offers lots of privacy and has direct access to the beach. Each bungalow has a queen-sized bed, terrace, day beds, flat-screen TV, tea/coffee maker, and a private outdoor shower. We also provide a mini-bar in the room with an all-inclusive meal package. Our restaurant offers international buffet meals and the Thila bar is by the swimming pool, you can enjoy sunsets while enjoying various alcoholic and non-alcoholic beverages. We are also providing a variety of professional diving courses through our joint partnership with Werner Lau and Divderland. In addition, there are also excursions such as island hopping and dolphin watching. At the spa, you can get relaxing massages and there are other activities such as table tennis, beach volleyball, darts, kayaking, and stand-up paddling. In addition, you will also have direct access to the reef for snorkeling and diving.
